CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,FThe Chair of Peak Cluster has said he
OL,7,Fis "very confident" the #5 billion gas
OL,8,Fpipeline will go ahead, despite
OL,9,Fprotests from residents in the Wirral.
OL,11,FHundreds of local residents gathered
OL,12,Foutside the town hall to protest the
OL,13,Fproposed 160-mile carbon capture
OL,14,Fpipeline that would run through
OL,15,FCheshire and the Wirral on 8 and 9
OL,16,FMarch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,FPeak Clusters Chair Dave Parkin said:
OL,7,F"The level of opposition on the Wirral
OL,8,Fin particular is considerably greater
OL,9,Fthan we have seen over this project
OL,10,Fanywhere else on the pipeline route.
OL,12,F"That is something we need to better
OL,13,Funderstand and work with."
OL,15,FHe said they have not been evasive and
OL,16,Fwanted to be transparent by working
OL,17,Fwith local councillors but added: "I
OL,18,Fthink it's unlikely we will end up on
OL,19,Fthe same page. All we can do is
OL,20,Fprovide evidence, facts, and what we
OL,21,Fare going to do.
OL,26,@uD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,F"If we can gain some local support
OL,7,Fthat would be ideal but I am not
OL,8,Fexpecting widespread public support
OL,9,Ffor this project."
OL,11,FWirral councillors unanimously decided
OL,12,Fto write to the UK Government as well
OL,13,Fas MPs to get the project - which
OL,14,Fwould see a carbon dioxide pipe built
OL,15,Ffrom the Peak District to the Irish
OL,16,FSea - scrapped.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,FCllr Mark Skillicorn said meeting Peak
OL,7,FCluster representatives was "tense"
OL,8,Fand "deeply troubling" as they "gave a
OL,9,Fvery strong impression that they do
OL,10,Fnot care".
OL,12,FMr Parkin said the meeting was
OL,13,F"engaging and we had a reasonable
OL,14,Fdiscussion."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,FHe added: "What is at the bottom of
OL,7,Fall of this and why the project team
OL,8,Fand in a way the local residents and
OL,9,Flocal councillors are talking past
OL,10,Feach other is this is a clash over a
OL,11,Fproject which is in the national
OL,12,Finterest which is meeting local
OL,13,Fopposition and how you navigate and
OL,14,Fget over that."
OL,16,FLocals have been critical of the
OL,17,Fproject over worries it could ruin the
OL,18,Fnatural landscapes and harm the
OL,19,Fwildlife.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,FBut the government says it is "vital"
OL,7,Ffor the country's future as it tries
OL,8,Fto meet its net zero targets, and have
OL,9,Frejected a petition signed by 17,000
OL,10,Fpeople to pause the project.
OL,12,FMr Parkin said scrapping the project
OL,13,Fis "not something that we have on the
OL,14,Ftable".
OL,16,FHe said Peak Cluster is "absolutely
OL,17,Fhappy to engage on every aspect of the
OL,18,Fproject but if the main discussion the
OL,19,Fcouncillors want to have is to move
OL,20,Fthe project elsewhere, that is not
OL,21,Fsomething we can give."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,FCampaigners argue the project will do
OL,7,Flittle to tackle climate change and
OL,8,Fhave a significant environmental
OL,9,Fimpact compared to alternatives.
OL,11,FPeak Cluster say the UK "urgently
OL,12,Fneeds more sustainable ways to produce
OL,13,Fthe essential materials we rely on
OL,14,Fevery day."
OL,16,FLaura Beveridge, from campaign group
OL,17,FAction Against CCS, said she thinks
OL,18,Fthe Peak Cluster "were not prepared"
OL,19,Ffor the public engagement aspect of
OL,20,Fthe project.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,FShe said: "Nothing he says will change
OL,7,Fhow we feel about the consultation.
OL,8,FThey are just going to push ahead. Let
OL,9,Fthem push ahead because the people of
OL,10,FWirral won't back down over this.
OL,12,F"I honestly think they have been
OL,13,Fbacked into a corner to hold a second
OL,14,Fconsultation. The feeling of residents
OL,15,Fon the Wirral is that this second
OL,16,Fconsultation is lip service and is not
OL,17,Ftrue engagement on Peak Cluster,
OL,18,Fespecially when they keep on
OL,19,Freiterating that this is going ahead.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,F"It seems like they want us to lie
OL,7,Fdown and go away. No one feels this is
OL,8,Fa genuine attempt at engagement. The
OL,9,Ffeeling is if they really wanted to
OL,10,Fengage with people genuinely ` to
OL,11,Frepeat these statements this is going
OL,12,Fahead and this is happening ` they
OL,13,Fwouldn't be saying that.
OL,15,F"They need to be held accountable. We
OL,16,Fdo not want this moved. We want this
OL,17,Fscrapped."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773778272
OL,3,CBoss 'very confident' pipeline will go
OL,4,Cahead despite protests
OL,6,FGovernment projections suggest the
OL,7,Fproject could protect up to 13,000
OL,8,Fjobs while the wider carbon capture
OL,9,Fsector could provide 50,000 jobs over
OL,10,Fthe next twenty years.
OL,12,FThe Peak Cluster CEO John Egan says
OL,13,Fthe Wirral was seen as the most
OL,14,Ffeasible route to the Irish Sea,
OL,15,Fchosen over areas from North Wales to
OL,16,FCumbria.
OL,18,FA final decision will be made on
OL,19,Fwhether the project goes ahead in 2029.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
